    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Arctium lappa are inflammation, which it reduces with its anti-inflammatory properties, and arthritis, a condition characterized by joint pain and stiffness that Arctium lappa's anti-inflammatory properties help alleviate. Arctium lappa also helps in treating digestive issues, such as diarrhea and constipation, due to its ability to stimulate intestinal contractions and improve bowel function. Additionally, Arctium lappa has been used to treat diabetes by lowering blood sugar levels and improving insulin sensitivity. Furthermore, it is effective in treating skin conditions like eczema and skin infections by reducing inflammation and promoting wound healing. Arctium lappa's anti-inflammatory properties also help in treating inflammatory bowel disease, gastroenteritis, and gastritis, while its diuretic properties can help alleviate kidney stones and fever.",
